com.apriori.di

Class Key<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.apriori.di.Key<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type represented by the key

    public class Key<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A key for binding injected types to their implementations. The key can be used for both halves of the binding -- the injected type and the definition of the binding target.
